OL,3,CBotched surgical tourism can cost NHS
OL,4,Cnearly #20,000 per patient, study finds
OL,6,FResearchers said they were also aware
OL,7,Fof reports of multiple organ failure
OL,8,Fdue to sepsis from wound infection,
OL,9,Fand death due to hypoxic brain injury
OL,10,Fand cardiac arrest.
