OL,3,CBotched surgical tourism can cost NHS
OL,4,Cnearly #20,000 per patient, study finds
OL,6,FExperts from Cardiff and Bangor
OL,7,Funiversities examined 37 studies, of
OL,8,Fwhich 19 included complications
OL,9,Ftreated by the NHS due to metabolic/
OL,10,Fbariatric surgery, 17 included
OL,11,Fcomplications due to cosmetic surgery,
OL,12,Fand one involved complications arising
OL,13,Ffrom eye surgery.
OL,15,FThe data included 655 patients treated
OL,16,Fby the NHS between 2011 and 2024 for
OL,17,Fcomplications.
