OL,3,CBotched surgical tourism can cost NHS
OL,4,Cnearly #20,000 per patient, study finds
OL,6,FResearchers calculated the NHS cost of
OL,7,Fpeople having their surgeries abroad
OL,8,Fand then needing care in the UK, with
OL,9,Ffigures ranging from #1,058 to #19,549
OL,10,Fper patient, although there was some
OL,11,Funcertainty over this evidence due to
OL,12,Favailable data.
OL,14,FOf those studies that reported length-
OL,15,Fof-stay in hospital, the maximum stays
OL,16,Fwere 45 and 49 days, with the average
OL,17,Ffor metabolic/bariatric surgery being
OL,18,F17 days.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G4/17
