OL,3,CBotched surgical tourism can cost NHS
OL,4,Cnearly #20,000 per patient, study finds
OL,6,FMost patients in the studies were
OL,7,Fwomen (90%), with an average age of
OL,8,F38, and the most common destination
OL,9,Ffor surgery was Turkey (61% of
OL,10,Fpatients).
OL,12,FThe most commonly reported procedures
OL,13,Fwere sleeve gastrectomy (where about
OL,14,F80% of the stomach is removed to leave
OL,15,Fa pouch), breast enlargement, and
OL,16,Ftummy tucks.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G5/17
