OL,3,CBotched surgical tourism can cost NHS
OL,4,Cnearly #20,000 per patient, study finds
OL,6,FOverall, 22 studies on 371 patients
OL,7,Freported more details on
OL,8,Fcomplications, with at least 196
OL,9,Fpatients (53%) in this research
OL,10,Fexperiencing moderate to severe
OL,11,Fcomplications.
OL,13,FThe study calculated hospital costs
OL,14,Fbut warned that extra costs, such as
OL,15,Fpeople seeing their GP, a nurse or
OL,16,Fpharmacist, were on top.
OL,18,FEmergency and semi-urgent surgery,
OL,19,Fdental and transplant surgery, cancer
OL,20,Ftreatment and fertility treatment was
OL,21,Falso excluded.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G6/17
