OL,3,CBotched surgical tourism can cost NHS
OL,4,Cnearly #20,000 per patient, study finds
OL,6,FThe authors said: "We still do not
OL,7,Fknow how many people resident in the
OL,8,FUK go abroad for elective surgery or
OL,9,Fhow many people subsequently
OL,10,Fexperience complications.
OL,12,F"Without these data, we cannot fully
OL,13,Funderstand the levels of risk that
OL,14,Fpeople seeking surgery abroad are
OL,15,Ftaking.
