OL,3,CBotched surgical tourism can cost NHS
OL,4,Cnearly #20,000 per patient, study finds
OL,6,F"Those seeking medical treatment
OL,7,Fabroad should be made aware of which
OL,8,Fcomplications the NHS is responsible
OL,9,Ffor treating, and costs for which the
OL,10,Fpatient may be potentially personally
OL,11,Fliable, including non-emergency
OL,12,Ftreatment."
OL,14,FThe authors said doctors in the UK
OL,15,Falso do not have access to full notes
OL,16,For know exactly what happened during
OL,17,Fsurgery when they are treating people.
