OL,3,CBotched surgical tourism can cost NHS
OL,4,Cnearly #20,000 per patient, study finds
OL,6,FWhen looking at why people go abroad,
OL,7,Fresearch suggests it may be because
OL,8,Fprocedures are not available on the
OL,9,FNHS, private operations are cheaper
OL,10,Fabroad, and NHS waiting times can be
OL,11,Flong.
OL,13,FThe number of medical tourists has
OL,14,Frisen steadily over the past several
OL,15,Fdecades, a trend that shows no sign of
OL,16,Fabating, the researchers said.
OL,18,FThe Royal College of Surgeons of
OL,19,FEngland (RCP) echoed calls for
OL,20,Fnational data on the problem.
