OL,3,CBotched surgical tourism can cost NHS
OL,4,Cnearly #20,000 per patient, study finds
OL,6,FRCP England vice-president Professor
OL,7,FVivien Lees said: "Too often people
OL,8,Fare drawn in by cut-price deals and
OL,9,Fglossy online marketing, only to
OL,10,Freturn with serious, sometimes life-
OL,11,Fchanging complications.
OL,13,F"When things go wrong, the NHS is left
OL,14,Fto pick up the pieces, often in
OL,15,Femergencies and without full
OL,16,Finformation about what surgery was
OL,17,Fdone or by whom.
