OL,3,CBotched surgical tourism can cost NHS
OL,4,Cnearly #20,000 per patient, study finds
OL,6,F"It should not be the role of the NHS
OL,7,Fto routinely mop up the mistakes of
OL,8,Fprivate providers overseas, and we
OL,9,Fwould encourage the Government to
OL,10,Fcontinue bringing pressure to bear on
OL,11,Fforeign providers and other
OL,12,Fgovernments, including to cover the
OL,13,Fcosts of complications that happen in
OL,14,Ftheir countries."
OL,16,FIn 2024, Health Secretary Wes
OL,17,FStreeting said he would work to
OL,18,Fimprove safety for Britons travelling
OL,19,Fabroad for cosmetic procedures in the
OL,20,Fwake of several deaths.
